# IOM website — deploy & git safety (automatic)

Repo: `F:\iom_website` → **https://iobjectm.com** (Vercel, branch `master`).

## When the user wants the site live

Run **only**:

```bash
npm run deploy
```

Do **not** run `npx vercel --prod` — the project hook **blocks** it. `npm run deploy` runs git checks, build, push, and Vercel automatically.

If the user says "deploy", "go live", "update the website", or "push to production" → run `npm run deploy` without asking them to remember commands.

Read **AGENTS.md** and **DEPLOY.md** if unsure.

## Git — never without explicit user approval

- Do **not** run `git stash -u`, `git stash push -u`, or `git reset --hard` (hook-blocked).
- Always **commit + push** before deploy; `npm run deploy` enforces this.

